Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.40,script,,0,0,0,,That was my middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.30,script,,0,0,0,,Let's go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.50,script,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.40,script,,0,0,0,,You used to wear those too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.90,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.50,script,,0,0,0,,Looks like middle schoolers from the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.70,script,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.50,script,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.20,script,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.60,script,,0,0,0,,He owns a tea shop in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.20,script,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.30,script,,0,0,0,,It sure is cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.80,script,,0,0,0,,You're right. It looks like it might snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.10,script,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:25.90,script,,0,0,0,,You must have left home very early to get here this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:30.00,script,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We just suddenly decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.80,script,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:35.60,script,,0,0,0,,I slept over at my brother's house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.50,script,,0,0,0,,I see. You guys must get along very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.40,script,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.50,script,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:48.90,script,,0,0,0,,That's just for a little change of mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.30,script,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.00,script,,0,0,0,,Well, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.30,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:01.20,script,,0,0,0,,Yes? Welcome. The usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:06.90,script,,0,0,0,,Yes, please. Oh yes, the shampoo you gave me last week, it's so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.80,script,,0,0,0,,Koshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.90,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.40,script,,0,0,0,,Do be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.30,script,,0,0,0,,I'm not a pro, so I'm not sure if I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.30,script,,0,0,0,,I think it's because a tile is cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.00,script,,0,0,0,,Could you at least try?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.70,script,,0,0,0,,The leak is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.10,script,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.50,script,,0,0,0,,Man, it's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.20,script,,0,0,0,,Is it fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.40,script,,0,0,0,,Probably... Actually, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.50,script,,0,0,0,,Eh, what? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.60,script,,0,0,0,,That's because the kid next door...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.40,script,,0,0,0,,Even if that's so, this is so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.10,script,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.70,script,,0,0,0,,You really do look like a middle schooler from the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.80,script,,0,0,0,,Just because there aren't many photos of you, brother. It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.40,script,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:24.40,script,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I found these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.60,script,,0,0,0,,Your collection of compositions from elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:34.00,script,,0,0,0,,Ah, mom, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.10,script,,0,0,0,,"My dream is to become a beautician."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:37.90,script,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:42.40,script,,0,0,0,,"That is because my mother is a beautician, so I want to take after her."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:47.30,script,,0,0,0,,"I will also get married. I want lots of children."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:52.40,script,,0,0,0,,"I will call my mother, father and brother and we'll all live together."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.20,script,,0,0,0,,"Then I think it will be a lot of fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.80,script,,0,0,0,,So she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.50,script,,0,0,0,,It does seem like a lot of fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.40,script,,0,0,0,,Your husband is going to have a tough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.20,script,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:26.00,script,,0,0,0,,Sorry for dropping in all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.00,script,,0,0,0,,Umm... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.70,script,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.40,script,,0,0,0,,You actually helped me out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.50,script,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I would like you to come everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.50,script,,0,0,0,,Bye then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.30,script,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.30,script,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.00,script,,0,0,0,,Should we commit lover's suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.80,script,,0,0,0,,I don't mind either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.20,script,,0,0,0,,If you're okay with it, then I don't care which.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.80,script,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:49.10,script,,0,0,0,,I can't decide which...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:10:00.30,script,,0,0,0,,I don't know... what to do... so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.20,script,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.70,script,,0,0,0,,If you're not sure, then let's just go home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:17.70,script,,0,0,0,,I think it's fine to go home and then think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.70,script,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.90,script,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.90,script,,0,0,0,,That's why I said that I'm fine as long as I'm with you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.09,ilmottelu,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,90)\frz18}Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:11:02.08,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in the end, we're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.48,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unable to find the answer to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.18,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the right thing to do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.08,script,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.08,script,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.48,script,,0,0,0,,You really did quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.68,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.38,script,,0,0,0,,I really did quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.38,script,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.08,script,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:45.58,script,,0,0,0,,You sure do have absolutely no direction in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:52.08,script,,0,0,0,,If you're not able to do anything anymore, then you should just come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.08,script,,0,0,0,,If I'm not able to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.08,script,,0,0,0,,Do you really think it'll solve itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:04.48,script,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I said that I wouldn't say anything anymore, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:10.08,script,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens... I can't wish you good luck, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.08,script,,0,0,0,,Stay well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.78,script,,0,0,0,,Bye, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.48,script,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Nanoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.98,script,,0,0,0,,Do you want to do some karaoke on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:44.88,script,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but there's somewhere I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.78,script,,0,0,0,,Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.48,script,,0,0,0,,She doesn't hang out with us much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.68,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.48,script,,0,0,0,,I bet it's a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.38,script,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.88,script,,0,0,0,,Probably, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.38,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.88,script,,0,0,0,,Do you want to follow her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.58,script,,0,0,0,,Let's follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.88,script,,0,0,0,,I want to see what kind of guy he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.88,script,,0,0,0,,Nanoka's boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.58,script,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:15.58,script,,0,0,0,,You guys peeped at my date!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.68,script,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.18,script,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.48,script,,0,0,0,,Let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.08,script,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of scared.
