Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:04.78,script,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.98,script,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:35.48,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one thing I do know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:45.68,script,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.68,script,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.38,script,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.68,script,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.98,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.18,script,,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.18,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is something that I don't want to let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.88,script,,0,0,0,,Do you have everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.58,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:33.68,script,,0,0,0,,Suburban shopping malls are the trend of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:39.18,script,,0,0,0,,But if this place is gone, then I think that many people will be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:44.18,script,,0,0,0,,Actually, there are more people in favor than in opposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.04,script,,0,0,0,,There isn't that kind of an institution around here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:50.17,script,,0,0,0,,I think many of the residents felt that it was inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.39,script,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:57.58,script,,0,0,0,,I feel that destroying the row of trees would be wasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:04.08,script,,0,0,0,,But I guess you can't do business with just sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:17:00.78,script,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:06.97,script,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.62,script,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.38,script,,0,0,0,,Come here, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.14,script,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.75,script,,0,0,0,,You rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.88,script,,0,0,0,,I'll go clean myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.09,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:04.83,script,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.01,script,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:28.73,script,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.21,script,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.25,script,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.88,script,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.38,script,,0,0,0,,Hurry, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.08,script,,0,0,0,,Amusement parks are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.38,script,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.58,script,,0,0,0,,...fun even if they aren't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.91,script,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.18,script,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.88,script,,0,0,0,,How disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.21,script,,0,0,0,,That it doesn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.92,script,,0,0,0,,I thought you said that it was fun even if it wasn't moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.30,script,,0,0,0,,The ferris wheel is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.05,script,,0,0,0,,You sure are hard to please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.68,script,,0,0,0,,But... it's better if it moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.58,script,,0,0,0,,I bet it would be beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:12.88,script,,0,0,0,,The town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:14.98,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.29,script,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we can't move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.52,script,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if we can move it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.08,script,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.02,script,,0,0,0,,By praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.62,script,,0,0,0,,Ehh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.32,script,,0,0,0,,You don't know unless you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.85,script,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:40.22,script,,0,0,0,,Come on, you try praying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.55,script,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:52.12,script,,0,0,0,,Don't give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.12,script,,0,0,0,,Come on, once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.72,script,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.69,script,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.95,script,,0,0,0,,We did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.85,script,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.55,script,,0,0,0,,Once more, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.55,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.75,script,,0,0,0,,Aren't we doing something stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.55,script,,0,0,0,,You're the one who started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.00,script,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.90,script,,0,0,0,,Ready? One... two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:12.85,script,,0,0,0,,Really... what are we doing?
