Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:49.52,script,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.41,ilmottelu,,0,0,0,,{\pos(255,200)\frz10\c&HA0A0A0}Nanoka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.41,ilmottelu,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,180)\frz10\c&HA0A0A0}Saeki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:55.45,script,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:02.85,script,,0,0,0,,Let's come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.02,script,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:06.14,script,,0,0,0,,Every year, when it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:07.88,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:10.11,script,,0,0,0,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:11.41,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:14.19,script,,0,0,0,,I'm going home then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.29,script,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take a bath at my place first?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:19.69,script,,0,0,0,,I'm fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:21.59,script,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:22.95,script,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:24.29,script,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:28.59,script,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:29.89,script,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:32.09,script,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:33.99,script,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:49.99,script,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:56.99,script,,0,0,0,,I love you!
